N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 109.5 - Court action or other legal process

State Regulations

With respect to any court action or legal process referred
to in section
109.4
(b)(2)
of
this Part, any interest obligation incurred by the authority after any of the
cut-off dates specified therein pursuant to any provision of law other than
this section shall be determined as prescribed by such other provisions of law, shall be paid as directed by the court, and shall be paid from any source of
funds available for that purpose. Notes
